descriptionHtml:
[center][color=#00ff00][size=6]OVERVIEW[/size][/color][/center][list]
[*][size=4]This a [color=#00ff00]High Fantasy[/color] [color=#00ffff]Racemenu [/color]and [color=#00ffff]ECE[/color] Preset.[/size]
[/list][size=4]
[/size][list]
[*][size=4]This also comes with [color=#00ffff]Nif[/color] files for those who only want the shape.[/size]
[/list][size=4]
[/size][list]
[*][size=4]I spent lots of time just sculpting characters (more than playing) and as i finally decided to start modding not too long ago i knew that I wanted to start sharing the characters i work on.[/size]
[/list][size=4]
[/size][list]
[*][size=4]If there are any [color=#ffff00]Problems[/color] with the files please let me know so i can diagnosis the problem. [/size]
[/list][size=4]
[/size][list]
[*][size=4]More to come so i hope you enjoy. Cheers[/size]
[/list]



[size=6][color=#00ff00]Requirements[/color]

[/size][list]
[*][color=#00ffff][size=4]KS Hairdos[/size][/color]
[*][color=#00ffff][size=4]SG Eyebrows[/size][/color]
[*][color=#00ffff][size=4]Lind's Human Eyes[/size][/color]
[*][color=#00ffff][size=4]Pure Skin  or Demoniac[/size][/color]
[*][size=4][color=#00ffff]Make-up is purely subjective and optional. I design all my preset(s) to not [/color][color=#ffff00]NEED[/color][color=#00ffff] make-up the focus is always [/color][color=#ffff00]Mesh[/color][color=#00ffff] first. [/color][/size]
[/list]
author: JlynOX
